## Task 3 – Notes

This task involved exploring different digital platforms and completing small activities to understand how they support learning and collaboration. Through this activity, I learned how online tools can be used to share information, collect responses, and participate in interactive tasks.

While working on this task, I gained practical experience using digital platforms and documenting the activity with screenshots as proof. It also helped me understand how such tools are commonly used in academic and professional environments for communication, collaboration, and data collection.

Overall, this task improved my confidence in using digital platforms effectively and responsibly.
